TextEng: Watch who you threaten, fool!
I have no idea who that is and I don't care!
Not my problem. Good luck. You'll need it.
Text: 내 알 바 아니야. 행운을 빌지. 필요할 거야.

TextEng: He's probably not coming back.
Shouldn't you go look for him?
Text: 그를 찾으러 가야 하는 거 아니야?

TextEng: I'll tell him if I see him. Good luck.
Text: 보게 되면 전해 줄게. 행운을 빌어.

TextEng: Sorry, I haven't seen him.
Hector? Yeah, he's here. A little out of sight though.
Text: 헥터? 응, 여기 있어. 좀 안 보이는 곳에 있지만.

TextEng: I saw him, but I didn't bring him with me.
He's got to be dead. There's no way he'd survive.
There may be a Helmite blessing sanctuary somewhere. I could lead you.
Text: 어딘가에 헬름의 성소가 있을 거야. 내가 안내해 줄 수 있어.

TextEng: I could escort you to the Shining Serpent. It's supposedly safe.
Text: 빛나는 구렁이까지 동행해 줄 수 있어. 거긴 안전하다고들 해.

TextEng: Your wagon is shot. You'd better make a run for it.
Text: 네 짐마차는 완전히 맛이 갔어. 도망치는 게 나을 거야.

TextEng: Tough break. Goodbye and good luck.
Well that's just rude. Don't make many friends, do you?
Text: 정말 무례하군. 친구 별로 못 사귀겠지?

TextEng: Easy, I'm not your enemy.
I no hurt you. What you mad for?
You talk too much! Me hit if you keep yelling!
Text: 너 말 너무 많아! 계속 소리치면 나 때린다!

TextEng: He dead, me think. No way he live.
Text: 죽었을 거야, 내 생각엔. 살 방법 없어.

TextEng: Me see him, but not bring him here.
Him here with us. You just don't sees him.
Text: 여기 우리랑 같이 있어. 너 못 보는 것뿐이야.

TextEng: I don't sees him.
Me don't knows him and me don't cares!
Dat tough. Bye bye.
Your wagon broke pretty good. Better run for it.
Text: 너 짐마차 많이 망가졌어. 빨리 도망가는 게 좋아.

TextEng: Me lead yous to Shining Serpent tavern, maybe?
Text: 나 너 빛나는 구렁이 여관으로 안내해 줄까?

TextEng: Maybe lead you to Helmite sanctuary? You want?
I say so if I sees him. Good lucks on you.
Text: 그를 보면 말해 줄게. 행운 있으라.

TextEng: Maybe you go look?
Him probably no gonna come back.
This not problem for me. Big lucks to you.
Text: 이건 내 일이 아냐. 행운 많이 빌어.
